      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 16:25:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列空袭和埃及警卫死亡加剧紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/israel-egypt-troops-exchange-fire-in-gaza-says-israeli-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名埃及士兵星期一在加沙边境与以色列军队发生冲突期间丧生，而以色列星期日的空袭则造成流离失所者营地至少 40 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，进一步加剧了因以色列与哈马斯战争而产生的地区紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/israel-egypt-troops-exchange-fire-in-gaza-says-israeli-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:55:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界上任职时间最长的央行行长将在罗马尼亚获得新任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/world-s-longest-serving-central-bank-chief-to-get-new-term-in-romania</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界上任职时间最长的央行行长罗马尼亚穆古尔·伊萨雷斯库 (Mugur Isarescu) 即将获得新的五年任期确认，议员们寻求在 6 月底之前就延长任期进行投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/world-s-longest-serving-central-bank-chief-to-get-new-term-in-romania</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:26:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西央行行长罗伯托·坎波斯·内托表示通胀预测将会改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/brazil-analysts-see-faster-inflation-into-2026-as-outlook-dims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行行长表示，消费者价格预测将有所改善，此前一项受到密切关注的调查显示，经济学家将 2024-2026 年通胀预期上调至进一步高于目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/brazil-analysts-see-faster-inflation-into-2026-as-outlook-dims</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:57:07 GMT</pubDate>
